reviewText: I love these movies. And to have all of them at once was great at a very good price.
A must have for your romantic comedy collection.
3 out of the 4 DVDs were damaged. DVDs would start and about 10 mins into the movie they would start to skip.
I enjoyed all four movies what's your number in particular it was a predictable but honest connection between the two.
Love all four of the movies. Great comedy, love movies.
This means war was great, reason we ordered...rest just a happy bonus.

When I saw these movies together, I just had to have them!! I had seen 3 of the 4 & What's Your Number was also a great movie. Each movie has its own dvd & they all play. I haven't had any problems yet.
love this selection of movies and i love action movies so my fav. was THIS MEANS WAR...came in perfect condition
Came in time! Very happy to watch these movie!
